ival-2017/id1258744398\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.knatten.AmphiFestival2017\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://gbgbeerweek.se/\">Beer Week</a> - The official app for Gothenburg beer festival <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/se/app/beer-week/id1094707718\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gbgbeerweek\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewSoftware?id=1072222649\">BPMTap</a> - A BPM tapper that works <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewSoftware?id=1072222649\">(​iOS)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.edu.cityu.minerals\">CityU Minerals</a> - A mobile virtual museum <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/cityu-minerals/id1164394395\">(iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.edu.cityu.minerals\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.edu.cityu.minerals\">CityU Mobile</a> - City University of Hong Kong official portal app <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/cityu-mobile/id750718911\">(iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.edu.cityu.mobile\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/conrad-wise/id1090322679\">Conrad Wise</a> - The all-knowing Conrad Wise <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/conrad-wise/id1090322679\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ConradWise\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/countinental/id1065815345\">Countinental</a> - An app for counting things <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/countinental/id1065815345\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Countinental\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://livingabook.com\">Criminal Mind</a> - Interactive story book <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mente-criminal-living-a-book/id924788775\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.livingabook.mentecriminal\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://livingabook.com\">Dark Forest</a> - Interactive book <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/mx/app/dark-forest-living-a-book/id695442145\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.livingabook.darkforest\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://deemapp.co/\">Deem</a> - The ultimate way to see movie reviews worldwide <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/deem-movies/id1057365760\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.deem\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/fusetools/FuseCloud\">FuseCloud</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/fusetools/FuseCloud\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">73</span></span></a> - A SoundCloud<sup></sup>® player that uses the free SoundCloud API <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/fusecloud/id1173516856\">(iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fuse.fusecloud&#x26;hl=en\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/gamecalculator/id952709405\">GameCalculator</a> - A custom game calculator for parties <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/gamecalculator/id952709405\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.GameCalculator\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.littleboat.gig\">Gig</a> - Discover local nightlife <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.littleboat.gig\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://guiadoop.com.br/download/\">Guias Doop</a> - Celebrity lifestyle guide. <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/br/app/guias-doop/id1235335392\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=br.com.guiadoop.fuse\">(Android)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://htgame.uk\">HatTrick</a> The official app for the card-driven soccer simulation Hat-Trick <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/cl/app/hattrick-companion-app/id1160945812\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.apps.hattrick\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.HowOld\">HowOld</a> - Find out how old or young you look <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.HowOld\">(Android​)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/klickle/id873427610\">Klickle</a> - Find stuff that’s happening now from local businesses <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/klickle/id873427610\">(​iOS)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://myopportunity.com/\">Opportunity</a> - A lead generation tool built inside of a business network <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/opportunity-business-opportunities/id1120189533\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.opprtunity.opprtunityapp\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.qubatetech.quotis\">Quotis</a> - Streamlined inspirational quote app that let's you browse and copy/paste great quotes <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.qubatetech.quotis\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://sanntidsappen.9u.no/\">Sanntidsappen</a> - Great-looking overview of bus routes in Trondheim <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/no/app/sanntidsappen/id1106042398\">(​iOS)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://snapptime.de/\">Snapptime</a> - Enjoy the food offers in your city (in German) <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/de/app/snapptime/id1162387536\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.snapptime\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/spindice3d/id1082656455\">SpinDice3D</a> - Select and spin a dice from collection of 4, 6, 8, 12 and 20 sides <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/spindice3d/id1082656455\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.SpinDice\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.tastyapp.tasty&#x26;hl=en\">Tasty</a> - The local food curation chatbot app <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.tastyapp.tasty&#x26;hl=en\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/no/app/teslactrls/id1120560798\">Tesla CTRL</a> - This app will give you better control of your Tesla <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/no/app/teslactrls/id1120560798\">(​iOS)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://livingabook.com\">The Monster and the Cat</a> - Interactive book <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/mx/app/the-monster-and-the-cat/id726779970\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.livingabook.monsterandcat\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tiffinity/id1191434201\">Tiffinity</a> - Order delicious home made food from around you <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tiffinity/id1191434201\">(​iOS)</a>. <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.apps.tiffinityapp\">(Android)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/bt/app/timecircle/id1068220814\">Timecircle</a> - Simple yet effective and good-looking stop watch <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/bt/app/timecircle/id1068220814\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vegardstrand.TimeCircle\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/timestealer/id1073144825\">Timestealer</a> - Track how much your meetings are costing you and your company <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/timestealer/id1073144825\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Timestealer\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/vaka/id1077345742\">Vaka</a> - Vaka is a game for focused and stable mind <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/vaka/id1077345742\">(​iOS)</a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Vaka\">(Android)</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://getwonder.io/\">Wonder</a> - An idea companion app that trains your creative and ideation skills <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/se/app/wonder-creativity-training/id1090880488\">(​iOS)</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"articles\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#articles\" aria-label=\"articles permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Articles</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@fusetools/a-sane-way-of-mixing-languages-in-fuse-660b351c2f96\">A sane way of mixing languages in Fuse</a> - Written by Chris Bagley.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.prototypr.io/do-we-need-better-prototyping-or-simpler-coding-269109426313#.7c7y1vgx7\">Do we need better prototyping or simpler coding?</a> - Written by Daniel Hollick.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@fusetools/fuse-foreign-speech-c4d888b505ec\">Fuse Foreign Speech</a> - Written by Remi Pedersen.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@fusetools/how-fuse-differs-from-react-native-and-nativescript-525344f02aaf#.pa1n8uh5l\">How Fuse differs from React Native and NativeScript</a> - Written by Remi Pedersen.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.creativitykills.co/how-to-add-infinite-scrolling-to-fuse-app/\">How to add infinite scrolling to fuse tools apps</a> - Written by <a href=\"https://github.com/neoighodaro\">Neo Ighodaro</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@fusetools/i-made-a-cross-platform-soundcloud-player-with-fuse-9fb1e62b7db1#.5lhmtwovz\">I made a cross-platform SoundCloud<sup></sup>® player with Fuse</a> - Written by <a href=\"https://github.com/kristianhasselknippe/\">Kristian Hasselknippe</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.prototypr.io/bots-wont-replace-apps-c88ff164990c#.2sp9vfqtv\">No, Bots are not killing apps (Bad apps are killing apps)</a> - Written by Anders Lassen.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://abduzeedo.com/interview-anders-lassen-fuse\">Interview with Anders Lassen from Fuse</a> - Written by <a href=\"http://abduzeedo.com/\">Abduzeedo</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://7sharpnine.com/2016/06/03/light-the-fuse/\">Light the fuse, using F# to write Fuse apps</a> - Written by <a href=\"https://github.com/7sharp9/\">7sharp9</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tmn.io/read/2015-11-22-making-mobile-apps-using-Fuse\">Making mobile apps using Fuse</a> - Written by <a href=\"https://github.com/tmn/\">Tri Nguyen</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/YugoCode/SwiftFuse/blob/master/README.md\">SwiftFuse</a> - Tutorial on how to use Swift with Fuse.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community\" aria-label=\"community permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 